{"type":null,"faqId":45056,"title":"WLAN速度慢或者信号差怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{color:black;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.06875in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">请您尽量不用手接触到手机的WLAN天线位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">如果您的手机距离WLAN路由器较远或者隔墙之后，信号强度会减弱，导致网速降低或者信号差。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">请确认是否使用了金属材质保护套，金属材质保护套对手机天线有影响，会导致手机信号变差，建议您使用塑料或皮质保护套。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">请确认所使用的路由器的规格，如果支持5G WLAN，请将路由器放置在比较高的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">请您检查是否同时有其它正在进行大数据使用的设备运行，如正在使用电视秘盒看电视、笔记本下载电影等，如有建议您合理分配网络资源。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">使用Speedtest或类似软件测试WLAN速率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span class=\"s2\">请您在靠近路由器的位置连接 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"557","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409491000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":24,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀WLAN,免费热点,信号差","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}